title: Championship Times Announced (Football)
text: Talk about it in Gridiron Talk The North Carolina High School Athletic Association announced the kick-off times for the 2015 championship games this year. Find out the dates, times, and places where each one will take place at, as we get closer to championship weekend.AT KENAN STADIUM, CHAPEL HILLFriday, Dec. 11
